      <name>Intelligence Summary</name>
      <Placemark>
        <name>AI Council Assessment</name>
        <styleUrl>#intel</styleUrl>
        <description>The current military posture and activity patterns suggest a high level of operational tempo in the Middle East, with a focus on supporting Operation Epic Fury. The deployment of carrier strike groups, amphibious ready groups, and destroyers indicates a significant naval presence in the region. The air campaign is being supported by a range of aircraft, including transport, ISR, and fighter assets. The use of hardened shelters and bunkers is becoming increasingly important, given the threat posed by Iranian air defenses. The overall assessment is that the US military is maintaining a high level of readiness and operational activity in the region, with a focus on supporting Operation Epic Fury and deterring Iranian aggression.</description>
        <Point>
          <coordinates>0,0,0</coordinates>
        </Point>
      </Placemark>
